  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    Publication scheme
  </h1>
</div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Information about the categories of information contained in the publication scheme.


  </p>

      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row ">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
        <div id="contents" class="app-c-contents-list-with-body">
    
        <div class="responsive-bottom-margin">
          
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Under the <a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2000/36/contents" title="Freedom of Information Act 2000">Freedom of Information Act 2000,</a> every public body in the UK must produce a publication scheme. The scheme makes it easy for you to access information about our activities.</p>

<h2 id="categories-of-information-in-the-publication-scheme">Categories of information in the publication scheme</h2>

<h3 id="who-we-are-and-what-we-do">Who we are and what we do</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dfid-organogram">DFID organisational chart</a></li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="https://data.gov.uk/organogram/department-for-international-development">DFID organogram on Data.gov.uk</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="organisations-we-are-responsible-for">Organisations we are responsible for</h3>

<p>We are responsible for the <a rel="external" href="http://cscuk.dfid.gov.uk/" title="Commonwealth Scholarship Commission">Commonwealth Scholarship Commission</a>, a non-departmental public body that awards scholarships and fellowships to Commonwealth citizens who wish to study in the UK.</p>

<h3 id="organisations-we-work-in-partnership-with">Organisations we work in partnership with</h3>
<p>We work with a wide range of organisations, both in the UK and internationally.</p>

<h3 id="organisations-we-sponsor">Organisations we sponsor</h3>
<p>We support organisations through our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/international-development-funding">funding opportunities</a>.</p>

<h3 id="targets">Targets</h3>
<p>We work towards achieving the <a rel="external" href="http://www.globalgoals.org/">Global Goals</a>.</p>

<h3 id="legislation">Legislation</h3>
<ul>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2002/1/contents" title="International Development Act 2002">International Development Act 2002</a> – sets out the legislative basis for our work</li>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2006/31/contents" title="International Development (Reporting and Transparency) Act 2006">International Development (Reporting and Transparency) Act 2006</a> – sets out the standards for reporting our progress against the Millennium Development Goals</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it">What we spend and how we spend it</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/about/statistics">Statistics on international development</a></li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/series/dfid-annual-report-2011-2012" title="DFID annual reports and accounts">Annual report and accounts</a> – primary financial statements recording the full costs of our activities, assets and liabilities, and how we’ve used resources to meet our objectives</li>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="http://devtracker.dfid.gov.uk/">Development Tracker</a> – financial information about our individual projects</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/series/ministerial-gifts-hospitality-travel-and-meetings-with-external-organisations-in-the-department-for-international-development" title="Ministerial gifts, hospitality, travel and meetings with external organisations">Ministerial gifts, hospitality, travel and meetings with external organisations</a></li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/international-development-funding">International Development Funding tool</a> – details of  funding schemes</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/about/procurement">Procurement</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="our-priorities-and-how-we-are-doing">Our priorities and how we are doing</h3>
<ul>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dfid-single-departmental-plan-2015-to-2020">Single Departmental plan</a> – sets out our vision and priorities</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/evaluations-completed-april-2015-to-march-2016">Evaluation reports</a> - evaluating the impact and lessons of our aid programmes.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="how-we-make-decisions">How we make decisions</h3>
<p>Visit <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/about/our-governance">Our governance</a> for information about the committees that advise on and monitor the decisions DFID’s ministerial team makes.</p>

<p>We recognise that when developing policies, <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=consultations&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-international-development&official_document_status=all&world_locations%5B%5D=all&from_date=&to_date=">consulting with a wide range of interested groups</a> helps us make sure we’ve taken into account the impact of the proposals on different sectors of society.</p>

<h3 id="our-policies-and-procedures">Our policies and procedures</h3>
<ul>
  <li>The <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dfid-smart-rules-better-programme-delivery">Smart Rules</a> provide the operating framework for the Department for International Development’s (DFID’s) programmes</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/blue-book-the-essential-guide-to-working-at-dfid">Rules and tools for staff</a> – guidance on rules, procedures and policies for all staff</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/blue-book-the-essential-guide-to-working-at-dfid">Policies and procedures for recruiting staff</a> – information on how we recruit staff</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/about/personal-information-charter">Personal data policy</a> – information on how we will handle your personal data and how you can access it</li>
  <li>Public enquiries – the Public Enquiry Point can answer many of your questions or put you in touch with other officials who can help</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/about/complaints-procedure" title="DFID's complaints procedure">Complaints procedure</a> – if you are dissatisfied with any part of the service DFID offers, you can lodge a complaint</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="services-we-offer">Services we offer</h3>
<ul>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="http://blogs.dfid.gov.uk/ebulletin-signup.html">E-bulletin</a> – our regular email update on the most important news from the international development world</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=all&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-international-development&world_locations%5B%5D=all&direction=after&date=2011-05-01">Leaflets, booklets, newsletters and other publications</a> – detail all aspects of our work</li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-international-development/about/petitions-and-campaigns">Your campaigns</a> – responses to campaigns coordinated by civil society groups</li>
  <li>
News – press releases and speeches by DFID ministers and officials</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="lists-and-registers">Lists and registers</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dfid-asset-management-strategy-december-2007">Capital assets – information on our buildings and other fixed assets, including their value</a></li>
  <li>
<a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dfid-freedom-of-information-disclosures">Freedom of Information (FOI) disclosure log</a> – information released in response to past FOI requests</li>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="http://data.gov.uk/publisher/department-for-international-development">Public data</a> – datasets we publish</li>
</ul>
</div>
